{"tid":1053393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳阿婆飲茶食雲吞鯁親昏迷送院","createTime":"2019-03-09T04:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T05:51:18.000Z","uid":6497,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9907943c70b9a406ab551888cc3907834e26ae","tid":1053393,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190309/s00001/c6971826b75ed568dae362cb672c5fba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190309%2Fs00001%2Fc6971826b75ed568dae362cb672c5fba.jpg&h=116249c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上11時01分，一名老婦偕兩名友人到將軍澳唐德街3號香港九龍東智選假日酒店內品茗期間，進食雲吞時懷疑鯁喉陷入昏迷，救護員接報到場為老婦急救，並送院搶救，警方正展開調查。據知，老婦送院時已沒有呼吸脈搏。"},{"pid":"f4538adc365f649259f5dd79c3c469f129cd4954","tid":1053393,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"死得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505985f6d9ecfaa712e8a4dd40bbe8bb378e2e7e","tid":1053393,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:24:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"152c31d5f8a420fc80b8d77e62bbafd9571f7724","tid":1053393,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:24:43.000Z","msg":"人類總要...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdce9d82f3b0fb5385dc45c18fe3dcbe0a1b975b","tid":1053393,"uid":10157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4538adc365f649259f5dd79c3c469f129cd4954","tid":1053393,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"死得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-